steps:
1. install debian buster lite from raspberry pi image installer
2. add empty file called "ssh" - this allows you to ssh initially
3. https://www.instructables.com/The-Ultimate-Headless-RPi-Zero-Setup-for-Beginners/


create file called wpa_supplicant.conf
```
ctrl_interface=DIR=/var/run/wpa_supplicant GROUP=netdev
update_config=1

network={
ssid="LeosPlace"
scan_ssid=1
key_mgmt=WPA-PSK
psk="Baconthebest"
}
```
